    {
      "chinese": "隨後李庥牧師在大社、愛蘭、內社各地，宣講所載耶穌的話語為了讓眾人相信，巴宰眾族人全都改變心意，隨後相信上帝，建立教堂。\r\n[---]\r\n牧師開始教巴宰族人學習羅馬字，巴宰族人學會讀聖經、吟唱敬拜的歌謠，熟練地寫著巴宰語，就因為這樣，巴宰眾族人記得巴宰語了！至今，巴宰的故事被後代有效地認知。感謝上帝。",
      "ab": "aubil a dali ka hada xaraw mudus Li-sio minusay dua dua razararaw kaidi Arux, Auran, Taba dua dua, pinidudu kinakawas no Yaso anu dadua saw paxi’ēdēr, Pazeh sasasaw ka madang henis dadua, liaka kaxiēdēr abababaw, minatu sasumadan. xaraw mudus maxa kasibat Pazeh saw dadēpēx bizu Lo-ma, Pazeh saw ka minabaza’ēn mēdēpēx sasumad a babizu, matoray masumad a araway, kinabazabaza bibizu’ēn rahal no Pazeh, maluhani lai ka, Pazeh a sawsaw ka padēria Pazeh a kakawas lia. taxu ohoni ka, Pazeh a pasukuan ka kabaza’ēn hawriak ni aubil a bazuah. pakadērēzaw Abababaw.",
